Takitimu gecko
Homonym Number:
Word Class: noun
Sense Number:
Definition:a rare gecko found from southern Fiordland to the Richardson Mountains; well camouflaged by bright herringbone patterning.
Origin: [none]
Register:
Register 2:
Domain: Environment
